track_notes: This track was for 2 summits when before Chabran as been deleted. There are some others path for this summit. Park is ok and lot of place on summit where is an animal park private for hunters!!!
I found a new path for this summit, witch is not difficult. The last 500 meters are very slope, you must follow the chain-link fence and use it to support the antenna if you like!
Park at the main road  and walk 200m to the bridge, the path is easy. get some water in summertime, there is a nice church St Jean du Desert.
